item.description:
HolyK's Blog https://blog.asukakyle.top/post/%E4%B8%87%E8%83%BD-euclidean-%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E5%B0%8F%E8%AE%B0/ -<h2 id="万能euclidean-算法">「万能」Euclidean 算法</h2>
<p><span class="math display">\[
F(P, R, Q, N, X, Y) = \prod_{i = 0}^N \left(Y^{f(i) - f(i-1)}X\right)
\]</span></p>
<p>其中 <span class="math inline">\(f(i) = \lfloor
\dfrac{Pi+R}{Q}\rfloor, f(-1) = 0\)</span>​。<span
class="math inline">\(X, Y\)</span>
<del>为操作序列，有乘法结合律，类比矩阵</del> <span
class="math inline">\(\in\)</span> <strong>半群</strong> <span
class="math inline">\((S, \times)\)</span>。</p>
<p>若 <span class="math inline">\(R \geq Q\)</span>​，则 <span
class="math inline">\(f(i)= \lfloor \dfrac{Pi+(R \bmod Q)}{Q}\rfloor +
\lfloor\dfrac{R}{Q}\rfloor\)</span>​，所以 <span class="math display">\[
F(P, R, Q, N, X, Y) = Y^{\lfloor\dfrac{R}{Q}\rfloor}F(P, R \bmod Q, Q,
N, X, Y)
\]</span></p>
<p>若 <span class="math inline">\(P \geq Q\)</span>​，则 <span
class="math inline">\(f(i)= \lfloor \dfrac{(P \bmod Q)i+R}{Q}\rfloor +
\lfloor\dfrac{P}{Q}\rfloor i\)</span>​，记 <span
class="math inline">\(f&#39;(i)= \lfloor \dfrac{(P \bmod
Q)i+R}{Q}\rfloor\)</span>​ <span class="math display">\[
\begin{aligned}
F(P, R, Q, N, X, Y)
&amp;= X\prod_{i = 1}^N Y^{f&#39;(i) -
f&#39;(i-1)}Y^{\lfloor\dfrac{P}{Q}\rfloor}X\\
&amp;= X\prod_{i = 0}^{N - 1} Y^{f&#39;(i+1) -
f&#39;(i)}Y^{\lfloor\dfrac{P}{Q}\rfloor}X\\
&amp;= XF(P \bmod Q, (P \bmod Q) + R, Q, N - 1,
Y^{\lfloor\dfrac{P}{Q}\rfloor}X, Y)
\end{aligned}
\]</span> 若 <span class="math inline">\(P &lt; Q\)</span>，考虑交换
<span class="math inline">\(X, Y\)</span>。</p>
<p>第 <span class="math inline">\(i\)</span> 个 <span
class="math inline">\(X\)</span> 前有 <span
class="math inline">\(f(i)\)</span> 个 <span
class="math inline">\(Y\)</span>，设第 <span
class="math inline">\(i\)</span> 个 <span
class="math inline">\(Y\)</span> 前有 <span
class="math inline">\(g(i)\)</span> 个 <span
class="math inline">\(X\)</span>， <span class="math display">\[
\begin{aligned}
g(i)
&amp;= \sum_{j \geq 0} [f(j) &lt; i+1]\\
&amp;= \sum_{j \geq 0} \left[\lfloor \frac{Pj+R}{Q}\rfloor &lt;
i+1\right]\\
&amp;= \sum_{j \geq 0} \left[ Pj+R\ &lt; Qi+Q\right]\\
&amp;= \sum_{j \geq 0} \left[j &lt; \lfloor \frac{Qi + Q-R + P - 1}{P}
\rfloor\right]\\
&amp;= \lfloor \frac{Qi + Q-R + P - 1}{P} \rfloor
\end{aligned}
\]</span> 但是末尾还有一些 <span class="math inline">\(X\)</span>​
后面没有 <span class="math inline">\(Y\)</span>​，需要单独拿出来 <span
class="math inline">\(X^{N+1 - \max g(i)}\)</span>。​​</p>
<p>于是 <span class="math display">\[
F(P, R, Q, N, X, Y) = F(Q, Q - R + P - 1, P, \lfloor \frac{PN + R}{Q}
\rfloor-1, Y, X)X^{N+1 - \max g(i)}
\]</span></p>
<p>复杂度为 <span class="math inline">\(O(T(S) \log N\log \min\{p,
q\})\)</span>，<span class="math inline">\(T(S)\)</span> 为 <span
class="math inline">\(S\)</span> 上的乘法复杂度。</p>
<h2 id="模板">模板</h2>
<p><code>S</code> 即半群 <span class="math inline">\((S,
\times)\)</span>
的结构体，这里假定它是幺半群（否则可以加一个幺元进去），则
<code>S()</code> 代表幺元。</p>
